## Provide sufficient contrast between foreground and background

Foreground text needs to have sufficient contrast with background colors. This includes text on images, background gradients, buttons, and other elements. 

This does not apply for logos or text that is in a photograph. 

You should meet a minimum contrast ratio of 4.5:1

### Guidance for meeting this standard

<a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/Understanding/contrast-minimum.html" target="_blank">WCAG 1.4.3 - Contrast (Minimum) Level - AA</a>

